A cyberpunk cityscape at night with towering neon-lit servers forming a dense urban jungle, where glowing data streams flow like rivers between buildings. In the foreground, a massive hexagonal hub structure pulses with electric blue energy, with dozens of luminous pathways branching outward in all directions like neural connections. Small drone-like particles carry packets of light along these routes, creating trails of cyan, magenta, and gold. The architecture combines industrial machinery with organic, vine-like cable bundles. Rain falls through holographic projection layers, creating prismatic light scattering. The scene conveys a sense of orchestrated chaos—countless independent systems working in harmony through an invisible communication network.
